Best Lead Generation Services

Lead generation services providers manage campaigns to discover and qualify customers for businesses, also known as leads. These services can be highly beneficial in filling an organization’s sales pipeline with potential clients; providers can also assist with establishing initial communications and building interest in the brand (demand generation). A number of these providers will assist with follow-up campaigns and other "lead nurturing" to ensure the best possible conversion rate. B2B lead generation services, or lead gen services, are typically used by sales departments but have proven to be beneficial for marketing teams when planning targeted outreach or generating new advertising efforts. Working with B2B lead generation companies can eliminate the guesswork of sales cold calls and present brands with high-quality leads (HQL) based on the brand’s ideal customer profile. This can streamline sales and marketing strategy, making sales quotas more easily attainable and setting the company up for success.

B2B lead generation services work as a supplement to or a replacement for in-house efforts using lead generation software such as lead capture software. Leads that are collected through an outsourced services provider can be further validated using lead intelligence software and lead scoring software. Lead lists that are assembled and delivered using these services can be uploaded into your organization’s CRM software to be organized, accessed, and updated throughout the sales lifecycle. Partnering with B2B lead generation services in conjunction with other outsourced services such as inbound marketing services and email marketing services can provide businesses with a robust source to gather and nurture leads.

To qualify for inclusion in the Lead Generation Services category, a provider must:

Perform customer profile creation interviews to better understand a company and determine its ideal target customers
Discover and source leads using one or more tactics, such as online research and content marketing
Qualify leads to ensure the information is correct and they are legitimate sales opportunities
Deliver complete lists of quality, verified leads
